1. Open below link,
              https://www.zaproxy.org/download/

2. Download Linux Installer 

3. Go to that download file directory and open terminal

4. Run Below command to make installer executable

              chmod u+x ZAP_2_14_0_unix.sh

              sudo ./ZAP_2_14_0_unix.sh

5. complate and finish the installation dialog box.
